import React from 'react';
import '../assets/styles/components/User.css'

const Tools = ()=> (
  <svg className="user" viewBox="0 0 650 650">
      <circle
        cx="313.65"
        cy="176.65"
        r="101.73"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#000"
        strokeDashoffset="300.69"
        strokeLinecap="square"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
        strokeWidth="40"
        paintOrder="markers fill stroke"
      ></circle>
      <ellipse
        cx="320.3"
        cy="592.76"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#000"
        strokeDashoffset="300.69"
        strokeLinecap="square"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
        strokeWidth="45.481"
        paintOrder="markers fill stroke"
        rx="192.43"
        ry="232.06"
      ></ellipse>
    </svg>
);

export default Tools;
